    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies new FTP commands to obtain listings of remote directories in a defined format, and to permit restarts of interrupted data transfers in STREAM mode.  It allows character sets other than US-ASCII, and also defines an optional virtual file storage structure. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
